moreApps.appDes: With IP TV Player, users can access various platforms that provide IPTV services. It offers features like adding content via M3U8 URL or Xtream Code, local file support, and easy navigation.

Are you tired of juggling between multiple media players to enjoy your favorite online content? Look no further! STV: Video Player is your all-in-one solution for seamless media streaming right on your Android device.
